Package de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.index.tree.spatial.rstarvariants.strategies.reinsert

Reinsertion strategies for R-Trees

See: Description


  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ReinsertStrategy
    Reinsertion strategy to resolve overflows in the RStarTree.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractPartialReinsert
    Abstract base class for reinsertion strategies that have a "relative amount" parameter to partially reinsert entries.
    AbstractPartialReinsert.Parameterizer
    Parameterization class.
    CloseReinsert
    Reinsert objects on page overflow, starting with close objects first (even when they will likely be inserted into the same page again!)
    CloseReinsert.Parameterizer
    Parameterization class.
    FarReinsert
    Reinsert objects on page overflow, starting with farther objects first (even when they will likely be inserted into the same page again!)
    FarReinsert.Parameterizer
    Parameterization class.
